<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/51797977-omer-dassa">Omer Dassa</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Some details that here are major parts of the premise were only revealed in the end of charmed life. So if you intend to read both it&apos;s better to star<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Some details that here are major parts of the premise were only revealed in the end of charmed life. So if you intend to read both it's better to start with #1. The plot and characters are sperate though.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
