<div id="review_1011262307" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1011262307" />
    <a title="Carolyn Klassen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4540420-carolyn-klassen"><img alt="Carolyn Klassen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1496695975p2/4540420.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1011262307?book_show_action=true">Jul 30, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Carolyn Klassen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Carolyn Klassen" href="/user/show/4540420-carolyn-klassen">Carolyn Klassen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4540420-carolyn-klassen?shelf=2020">2020</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4540420-carolyn-klassen?shelf=2014">2014</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1011262307" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10403454934580572562">This is a fun one, though probably my least favourite of the Chrestomanci books. I enjoy The Goddess, Throgmorton, and Tacroy, but I don&apos;t feel all that connected to the actual plot. A bit too long, perhaps. Still, I enjoy revisiting when I reread the whole series!</span>
  <span id="freeText10403454934580572562" style="display:none">This is a fun one, though probably my least favourite of the Chrestomanci books. I enjoy The Goddess, Throgmorton, and Tacroy, but I don't feel all that connected to the actual plot. A bit too long, perhaps. Still, I enjoy revisiting when I reread the whole series!</span>
  <a data-text-id="10403454934580572562" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

