<div id="review_3574941491" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3574941491" />
    <a title="Carmen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/48058841-carmen"><img alt="Carmen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1547856912p2/48058841.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3574941491?book_show_action=true">Nov 22, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Carmen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Carmen" href="/user/show/48058841-carmen">Carmen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48058841-carmen?shelf=women-of-the-world">women-of-the-world</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48058841-carmen?shelf=europe">europe</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48058841-carmen?shelf=2020">2020</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48058841-carmen?shelf=children-infantil-juvenil">children-infantil-juvenil</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48058841-carmen?shelf=fantasy-fantas%C3%ADa">fantasy-fantasía</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3574941491" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7458427001922753775"><blockquote>&quot;People only want either of us for what <i>use</i> we are to them!&quot; she sobbed. &quot;You for your nine lives and me for my Goddess atributes. And both of us are caught and struck and <i>trapped</i> in a life with a future all planned out by someone else-like a long, long tunnel with no way <i>out</i>!&quot;</blockquote><br/><br/>I really love Diana Wynne Jones&apos; books!</span>
  <span id="freeText7458427001922753775" style="display:none"><blockquote>"People only want either of us for what <i>use</i> we are to them!" she sobbed. "You for your nine lives and me for my Goddess atributes. And both of us are caught and struck and <i>trapped</i> in a life with a future all planned out by someone else-like a long, long tunnel with no way <i>out</i>!"</blockquote><br /><br />I really love Diana Wynne Jones' books!</span>
